%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Phong-t%E1%BA%ADt-chu-trung-ph%E1%BB%A5c-ch%E1%BA%A9m-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BA%ADn-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%93-Nam-th%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-maRxAMOCboIbSdvxXl781Q">Phong tật chu trung phục chẩm thư hoài tam thập lục vận, phụng trình Hồ Nam thân hữu - 風疾舟中伏枕書懷三十六韻，奉呈湖南親友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93/poem-0HE9KmVtI6MzgnIFqADRwg">Tây Hồ - 西湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/author-s5no_WN-Qbyowo0KXT53Zg">Dương Bang Bản</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-chi%E1%BA%BFn-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ca/poem-r-0sKzn4t1sF64MC4QGgRg">Thạch tướng quân chiến trường ca - 石將軍戰場歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-QwR8mfkWimm7tarlC84k4w">Lý Mộng Dương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-T%E1%BA%A5n/V%C5%A9/poem-9GKR-qKaIbKg2GsiGc8q5A">Vũ - 雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-S0vEItadDGBpDb_EczBqqg">Hoàng Tấn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
